Petra Wetzel is a divorcee who lives in Glasgow with her son, Noah, nine . 
  She set up her own business, the WEST brewery, in 2006 . 
  She runs one of Britain’s most successful small breweries . 
  Petra was inspired to start her business when her father visited Glasgow and she realised the city didn’t have its own brewery . 
  She is nominated for Mumpreneur Of The Year Award . 
 